Description: Software wireless CarPlay receiver for rootless jailbreaks.
 Showcase turns a jailbroken cellular iPad into a pure-software wireless
 CarPlay receiver. This package targets rootless iOS 15-17 jailbreaks and
 installs under /var/jb with iphoneos-arm64 package metadata.
 .
 First officially working rootless build. iPhone-specific UI tweak for
 the receiver app running on a jailbroken iPhone.
